  "title": "🎉 Events & Sales Crew",
  "description": "<p><em><strong>No desk. No boring days. All vibes.</strong></em></p><p><em><strong>Hate sitting still? Love talking to people? Want a job that actually feels alive?</strong></em></p><p><em><strong>Welcome to Events & Sales where work feels like an experience.</strong></em></p><p></p><p><u><strong>What you’ll be doing:</strong></u></p><p>🎪 Working events, roadshows & pop-ups</p><p>👋 Talking to people IRL (yes, face-to-face)</p><p>🔥 Promoting cool brands & campaigns</p><p>📈 Learning sales, confidence & people skills</p><p>💰 Earning based on performance (effort = income)</p><p>🌍 Traveling for events & team trips</p><p><br /><u><strong>This role is for you if:</strong></u></p><ul><li>You’ve got energy for days ⚡</li><li>You’re a people person (or want to become one)</li><li>You’re tired of boring 9–5 jobs</li><li>You want growth, not “just experience”</li></ul><p><u><strong>Perks:</strong></u></p><p>✨ Fun team culture</p><p>✨ Mentorship & personal development</p><p>✨ Unlimited earning potential</p><p>✨ Real career progression (not empty promises)</p><p><br /><em><strong>No experience? No problem.</strong></em></p><p><em><strong>Bring the attitude — we’ll teach the skills.</strong></em></p><p><em><strong>👉 DM us / Apply now and let’s make work fun 🚀</strong></em></p>",
